                        <interp inst="t18400817-name-406" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN PEARSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a gardener, and lire in Hackney-road. I saw Mallars and the big boy behind the prosecutor, and Sturgeon was before him—I saw the bigger boy lift up the prosecutor's pocket, and try to pick it—they followed him to Haggerston church, and there they did it—I saw the other boy's hand on the pocket—I cannot say that I saw the pocket picked—they were all three in company.</p>
